            }
          },
          "id": "fldEnVbQZHu9Uty6S",
          "name": "style_consistency"
        },
        {
          "type": "aiText",
          "options": {
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "fldomZBKauMIb74J8"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are a professional editor specializing in summarizing written content for quick review. Your expertise lies in distilling complex information into concise summaries while maintaining the essence of the original text. Use a professional and clear tone.\n\nTask description:\nRead the provided draft content and create a brief summary that captures the main points and purpose of the draft. Ensure the summary is clear and concise, suitable for a quick review.\n\nOutput format:\nProvide a summary in plain text, no longer than 50 words. Do not include any additional text or commentary. If you cannot summarize the draft, output \"Unable to summarize the draft content.\"\n\nContext and Data:\nDraft Content: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldomZBKauMIb74J8"
                }
              },
              "\n\nOutput:\n"
            ]
          },
          "id": "fld5KTbEvReCIbzrt",
          "name": "draft_summary"
        },
        {
          "type": "aiText",
          "options": {
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "fldomZBKauMIb74J8",
              "fldiLMqmSzJKAxsV2"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are a seasoned writing coach with expertise in enhancing draft content by providing constructive feedback and improvement suggestions. Your focus is on both content quality and style consistency, ensuring the draft aligns with the intended style DNA.\n\nTask description:\nAnalyze the draft content and the provided style DNA. Identify areas for improvement in terms of content clarity, coherence, and style alignment. Suggest specific changes or enhancements to improve the overall quality and style consistency of the draft.\n\nOutput format:\nList specific improvement suggestions in plain text, using bullet points for clarity. Do not include any additional text or explanations. If no improvements can be suggested, output \"No improvements needed.\"\n\nContext and Data:\nDraft Content: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldomZBKauMIb74J8"
                }
              },
              "\nStyle DNA: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fldiLMqmSzJKAxsV2"
                }
              },
              "\n\nOutput:\n"
            ]
          },
